0.2 (2026-04-24)
- Rewritten to use a Python logging handler instead of core patches
- Zero changes to weewx core required
- Added CSV output option
- Added MQTT output option (requires paho-mqtt)
- All outputs configurable via [RsyncMetrics] in weewx.conf
- 25 unit tests covering all output paths and edge cases

0.1 (2026-04-20)
- Initial release (required patches to rsyncupload.py and reportengine.py)
